With 56 glaucoma events and 8 handcrafted features (4 amplitude bins per color
from \texttt{featuresSimple.yaml}), our events-per-variable ratio is $\text{EPV} = 7.0$,
meeting minimum guidelines for prediction model development~\citep{riley_calculating_2020}.
For MOMENT embeddings (96 dimensions), $\text{EPV} = 0.58$ precludes reliable inference;
embedding-based results should be interpreted as exploratory.
